<h3>Weekly Rhythm Tips</h3>
<p>Publish on Monday, Wednesday, and Friday for maximum indexing spread. Google processes new content faster when it arrives at predictable intervals.</p>
<p>Use Tuesday and Thursday for production work. Drafting, editing, <a href="/blog/optimize-content-for-seo/">optimizing content for SEO</a>, and scheduling social promotion.</p>
<p>Reserve 1 slot per week for content refreshes. <a href="/blog/content-decay-fix/">Content decay</a> is real. Pages lose 30% of their traffic within 12 months without updates.</p>
