<h3>How to Use the Quarterly Plan</h3>
<p>Start by identifying 3 to 4 keyword clusters for the quarter. Map each cluster to a pillar page.</p>
<p>Then assign 3 to 5 supporting posts per cluster. Each supporting post links to its pillar and to at least 2 other posts in the cluster. This builds the <a href="/blog/internal-linking-blog-posts/">internal linking</a> structure that Google uses to understand your site architecture.</p>
<p>Alternate cluster focus week by week. Do not publish 4 "Content Ops" posts in a row and then ignore "SEO Strategy" for a month.</p>
